collection.name: Long Neckie Ladies
collection.description:
"If I can do it, you can do it"

A collection for dreamers, created by 13-year-old Nyla Hayes.

25+ ETH used to support #NFTKIDSART

Long Neckie Ladies is a fine art, hand drawn, computer generated collectible of 3,333 diverse
and elegant females. Each Long Neckie Lady features an elongated neck inspired by Nyla’s
favorite dinosaur, the brontosaurus.

Nyla Hayes made history in 2021 as TIME Magazine’s 1st NFT Artist in Residence, and has
been SEEN on CNN, Yahoo Finance, Business Insider, Investing.com, Black Enterprise,
AfroTech, and other outlets. Awards include NFT.NYC 2021 Emerging Artist of the Year,
Future 50’s most influential people in tech in 2021, and more.
